<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Homicide is also a multi-causal problem. Contrary to popular perception, the majority of firearm homicides are not the result of “stranger danger crime,” but rather the result of intimate partner violence or an argument between people who<br>
